Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:41.36,main,Luther,0,0,0,,为什么我还活着？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.67,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Dantalion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:53.00,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:55.67,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我败给了那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.22,main,Luther,0,0,0,,葬身于此才是理所应当的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:02.74,main,Luther,0,0,0,,但你却为了我这条无聊的命送死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.21,0:02:07.52,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,虽然我很欣赏你能抱有这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.77,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,但请你不要小看了我的觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.91,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,虽然你是这副样子，但看来你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.98,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:26.79,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,看啊，Luther，没死成不也挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:30.04,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,我们都能与各自的宿敌死战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.45,0:02:32.29,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Snow的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:35.05,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我再问你一次，你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.63,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:39.55,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Wisteria·Langley
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.80,italics,Luther,0,0,0,,她身上有历经死战的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:46.05,italics,Luther,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道这么短的时间里她经历了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:49.48,italics,Luther,0,0,0,,但她身上有一种在加害者手中为了活下去不惜脏了手的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:52.31,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我认可你作为我的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:54.45,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我不会再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.41,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:57.80,main,Wis,0,0,0,,好的，Marbas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.32,0:03:02.32,main,Luther,0,0,0,,限定解临，尸山蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:07.81,main,Luther,0,0,0,,战灾，Dantalion
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.47,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,小子，保护好 Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:37.48,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,怎么了？你在因为太担心那个丫头无法集中注意力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.48,0:03:39.99,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.01,0:03:51.01,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,对不起了，陪我去那里打吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.00,main,Snow,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:57.88,main,Snow,0,0,0,,那家伙把牛头人拖走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.88,main,Luther,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.89,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我就可以专心和我的对手死斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:12.85,main,Luther,0,0,0,,好好瞄准啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.73,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你还在手下留情吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.60,0:04:21.40,main,Wis,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:27.41,main,Luther,0,0,0,,不错的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.13,0:04:33.41,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你还记得吗，我曾说过终有一天我要和你打一架
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:38.17,main,Luther,0,0,0,,愿望终于实现了，真是高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:41.80,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我也是。这次不再是想想而已了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:44.55,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我要真的把你撕碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:50.81,main,Luther,0,0,0,,真不错，让我们全力厮杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:54.32,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,你似乎不怕死一样的解临了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:57.56,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我可不会再手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:01.07,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,你这是在低看我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:13.24,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,呐，Marbas，你想过了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:15.88,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,无论是什么样的契约者，终有一天他们都会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:17.88,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,除此之外，别无他选
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:23.23,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,特别是身为战士的 Luther，他肉体的巅峰时间很短
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:27.38,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,并且他自己是最清楚这一点的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:32.22,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,因此，我就是为了这个时刻活到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:35.64,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,Calamity Rain\N灾祸之雨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.70,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,你以为那种程度的攻击能防的住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.35,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.27,0:05:51.39,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,为了保护我该保护的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.86,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,为了保护我的心爱之物，我来了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:57.16,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:03.30,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我是为了让我和 Wisteria 在一起的日子更长而战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:06.30,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我没打算被不怕死的家伙打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:10.18,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Hell Lance\N炎狱之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:19.37,main,Wisteria,0,0,0,,没、没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:21.93,main,Snow,0,0,0,,Wis！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:23.59,main,Luther,0,0,0,,已经这样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.08,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我们持有的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:30.82,main,Luther,0,0,0,,是为了控制与我们契约的恶魔的力量不至于暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:34.57,main,Luther,0,0,0,,当然，恶魔使用的力量越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:37.23,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我们肉体的负担就越大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.84,main,Luther,0,0,0,,看起来你坚持不了多久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:44.09,main,Snow,0,0,0,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:47.59,main,Snow,0,0,0,,站起来，Snow，做不到的话就滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:50.27,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我要了结那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.72,main,Snow,0,0,0,,休想再从我身边夺走重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:01.10,main,Wis,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.36,main,Wis,0,0,0,,哥哥，哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:07.78,main,Luther,0,0,0,,无论是家人，还是同伴，或是正义之心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:11.86,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你们身上的包袱太多了，我看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:18.62,main,Snow,0,0,0,,为什么会变成现在这样，我想过很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.60,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我已经不再是你认识的那个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:25.88,main,Luther,0,0,0,,虽然很对不起，但我对现在的自己很满意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:30.63,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Snow，我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.36,main,Luther,0,0,0,,对只记得战场的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:37.14,main,Luther,0,0,0,,只有你和  Watson 医生不会区别对待我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:40.64,main,Luther,0,0,0,,所以我装作很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.15,main,Luther,0,0,0,,直到我遇到 Dantalion 之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.55,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你还是下不去手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.77,main,Luther,0,0,0,,当你在酒吧里察觉到恶魔时
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.41,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你就该立即去叫同伴来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:58.32,main,Snow,0,0,0,,啰嗦，我很清楚我就是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:07:59.66,main,Snow,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:04.70,main,Snow,0,0,0,,但我一想到这有可能是我们三人在一起的最后时光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:08.60,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我之前就发现你和以前不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:13.55,main,Snow,0,0,0,,即便你失忆了，正因为你还是你，我才陪着你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:17.30,main,Snow,0,0,0,,这可不是出于同情或者是想帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:19.50,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我们难道不是知音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.56,main,Snow,0,0,0,,无论是我，还是 Watson 医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:23.32,main,Snow,0,0,0,,就算是你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.17,0:08:27.06,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我现在也是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:30.07,main,Luther,0,0,0,,这都算些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:34.53,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你明明和我一样在战争中弄脏了手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.07,main,Luther,0,0,0,,见过了地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:41.37,main,Luther,0,0,0,,竟然还敢说那种漂亮话，你这个虚伪的圣职者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:44.12,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,这是.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:46.13,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Dantalion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:48.63,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Dantalion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:52.89,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你怎么一脸阴郁啊，老大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:54.88,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,Luther
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:58.14,main,Luther,0,0,0,,别磨蹭了，陪我到最后一刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:01.89,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,你已经不在乎生命了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:05.89,main,Luther,0,0,0,,连值得付出生命的事都不做，还谈什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:13.93,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,没错，从一开始就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.06,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.21,main,Diana,0,0,0,,我们快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.16,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:29.54,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,他认真的吗，他还打算进一步解临吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:33.92,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,Marbas，你说过我们在寻死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:36.48,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.48,0:09:40.68,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,我们才真正成为了寻死之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:44.68,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我在毫无节制地燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:49.80,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,我们要在绝佳状态中死去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.21,main,Luther,0,0,0,,现在开始第二轮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:11.03,main,Luther,0,0,0,,让我们享受着最后的战……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.71,0:10:12.88,main,Snow,0,0,0,,Luther
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:15.37,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,别靠近，小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.37,0:10:16.34,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Marbas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:20.09,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,这就是你想要的吗，Dantalion？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.41,main,Snow,0,0,0,,你还好吗，Wis
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:26.14,main,Wis,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.16,main,Snow,0,0,0,,喂，大猫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:35.16,main,Snow,0,0,0,,你不算用超厉害的烈焰猫猫拳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.65,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我没这技能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:41.74,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,尽可能远离这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.45,main,Snow,0,0,0,,大猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.30,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Marbas
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.60,italics,Marbas,0,0,0,,现在普通的攻击已经不起作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.94,italics,Marbas,0,0,0,,如果我有足够的时间发射炎狱之枪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.23,italics,Marbas,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:15.29,italics,Marbas,0,0,0,,该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.44,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.44,0:11:21.20,main,Luther,0,0,0,,正因为你们背负的东西太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:23.35,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你们是战胜不了我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.08,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria，快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.60,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.26,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,真是千钧一发啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.46,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Naberius
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.54,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,你的攻击为什么软趴趴的啊，臭猫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.54,0:11:42.90,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,对面可是在拼死战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:44.22,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,给我全力应对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:47.94,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,就算我想，我也没机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.94,0:11:49.98,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,你是瞎了吗，杂种狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:53.15,main,Wis,0,0,0,,那、那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:54.73,main,Diana,0,0,0,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:56.61,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Diana 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.61,main,Diana,0,0,0,,我来偿还之前的人情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.91,main,Diana,0,0,0,,没错吧，Naberius
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:03.86,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.49,main,Diana,0,0,0,,限定解临，冥府狂啸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:18.50,main,Diana,0,0,0,,地灾，Naberius
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:21.11,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Naberius，你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:23.76,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,我和 Diana 来争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:27.89,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,你用强大一击来终结战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.14,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,不必多言
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:34.64,main,Luther,0,0,0,,终究只是限定解临，根本不是 Dantalion 的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:36.56,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.45,0:12:46.20,italics,Naberius,0,0,0,,怎么样，砍到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:48.95,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Naberius
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.67,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Marbas，快点开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.67,0:12:55.21,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.60,0:12:57.71,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.47,0:13:12.63,main,Luther,0,0,0,,让我也来参一脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:18.31,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,该死，连契约者的力量都被增强了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:25.32,italics,Naberius,0,0,0,,还要保护 Diana，很难打了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.58,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,Astaroth
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.83,main,Astaroth,0,0,0,,啊，糟了糟了，这种热血的展开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.33,main,Astaroth,0,0,0,,我可不是自愿来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.92,0:13:37.83,main,Astaroth,0,0,0,,我的契约者带点个人恩怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.50,0:13:51.10,main,Luther,0,0,0,,Dantalion
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.12,main,Sol,0,0,0,,Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:04.73,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,他已经无法控制自己的力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.92,main,Sol,0,0,0,,攻击其中一个的话，另一个就会被动摇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.92,0:14:12.24,main,Sol,0,0,0,,我正在利用的就是你们之间的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.77,main,Sol,0,0,0,,被你所鄙视的我们的战斗方式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.77,0:14:20.35,main,Sol,0,0,0,,似乎足以分散你同伴的注意力了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.74,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:26.76,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我、我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.01,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我还能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:33.05,main,Luther,0,0,0,,你真敢搞这种小手段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:37.85,main,Luther,0,0,0,,老大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:43.28,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,已经够了，恐怕到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:47.13,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,不对，是不需再留念后事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:52.28,main,Astaroth,0,0,0,,那家伙难道想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:56.04,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,看这架势，他是要毁掉一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:58.79,main,Wis,0,0,0,,Marbas
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.79,main,Wis,0,0,0,,如果不是因为各位的话，不是因为你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.05,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我是不会变得坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.59,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我肯定不会站在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:11.30,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我们不是孤身一人的，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:14.30,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,没错，大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.31,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,并且，我也在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.76,0:15:44.08,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Dantalion，很不巧我没打算陪你赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:47.59,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我接下来会和 Wisteria 一起活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.55,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我不会选择在这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.34,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,对不起了，请你先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:59.63,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Hell Lance\N炎狱之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.43,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,我很享受，Luther
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:30.13,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,但遗憾的是我们没赢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.55,main,Luther,0,0,0,,别在意，将军大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.96,0:16:36.89,main,Luther,0,0,0,,我已经习惯了打败仗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:41.62,main,Dantalion,0,0,0,,没什么，这只是身为友人的遗言而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:55.91,main,Luther,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:00.66,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,随心所欲的大闹后，还算是不错的结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.66,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.77,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:28.94,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,但在城市和许多人的心中，仍还有伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.59,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,但终有一天，一切都会复原如初
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:36.95,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,Holmes 先生曾说过，人类是超乎想象的坚强的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:42.83,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,Luther 先生似乎失去了对那场战斗的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:44.53,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,以及关于 Dantalion 的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.04,italics,Wis,0,0,0,,然后，我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:51.54,main,Diana/Wis,0,0,0,,野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.13,main,Diana,0,0,0,,这家店的料理，特别美味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:57.90,main,Wis,0,0,0,,真的很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.90,0:18:00.09,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我为什么又和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.09,0:18:01.55,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,我也想问
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.69,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,但说起来你真是古怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:09.31,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,你明明都因为 Sitri 和 Dantalion 陷入过麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:12.20,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,却还想去见剩下的荒原十三灾厄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.78,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,你在发什么神经啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:16.82,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,只是想和他们聊聊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.50,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我们同为活了如此久的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:23.76,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,都在想些什么，过着什么样的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:28.56,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,说起来，我没喊你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:31.19,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,谁说我要一起去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:34.33,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,我们的要去找三眼恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.84,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,只是同一个方向而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.84,0:18:39.36,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,那你向西走，我向东走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:43.23,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,生活在日落处的都是些阴郁的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:44.74,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,你给我去西边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:45.60,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:47.54,main,Diana,0,0,0,,他们还是小孩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:52.01,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我很高兴又能和 Diana 你们一起去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.86,main,Wis,0,0,0,,不过又要和哥哥分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:59.82,main,Snow,0,0,0,,分开？你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.82,0:19:01.73,main,Snow,0,0,0,,哥、哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.73,0:19:03.45,main,Takenami,0,0,0,,你好啊，Wisteria 妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.88,main,Wis,0,0,0,,真的是哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.38,0:19:08.45,main,Takenami,0,0,0,,是 Snow 本人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:10.36,main,Diana,0,0,0,,但为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:13.65,main,Takenami,0,0,0,,你觉得我们会对两个大恶魔放之不管吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.14,0:19:18.88,main,Takenami,0,0,0,,但虽说如此，我们现在没有歼灭你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.44,main,Snow,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:26.25,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我们奉团长的命令与你们同行并监视你们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.25,0:19:28.45,main,Wis,0,0,0,,团长下的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.57,flashback,Sol,0,0,0,,什么啊，你的角复原了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:34.46,flashback,Marbas,0,0,0,,我也没想到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:36.93,flashback,Marbas,0,0,0,,但契约仍然需要履行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.93,0:19:41.11,flashback,Marbas,0,0,0,,不收取一点代价的话，会违反规则的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:43.49,flashback,Sol,0,0,0,,那你想要什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:48.24,main,Snow,0,0,0,,Wis，不用再担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:52.12,main,Snow,0,0,0,,我会从害虫，不对，是从大猫手中保护你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:54.66,main,Wis,0,0,0,,明明和虫子或者大猫都没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.13,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,这真是给不顺眼的小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.38,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我今天特别开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:02.10,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,意料之外的热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:10.78,main,Wis,0,0,0,,但能和你这样安静地交谈，我特别喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.66,main,Wis,0,0,0,,就像我们相遇时那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:16.99,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我有一件很在意的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:22.66,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Dantalian 那家伙消失的时候，你为何哭泣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:28.02,main,Wis,0,0,0,,虽然我对他们知之甚少
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:32.66,main,Wis,0,0,0,,虽然他们做了伤天害理的事，我不应当同情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:38.70,main,Wis,0,0,0,,但一想到我和 Marbas 终有一天会像他们一样分别
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:41.16,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:46.15,main,Wis,0,0,0,,这样想，很奇怪吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.73,0:20:50.88,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,不，我有时也会想一些奇怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.82,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,比如取回你的视力之类的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.55,0:21:00.69,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,或者可以的话，比你先死之类的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.04,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:08.13,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,看来我才是那个奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.78,main,Wis,0,0,0,,变得奇怪是没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.55,0:21:14.68,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我们是恶魔与契约者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:17.59,main,Wis,0,0,0,,是无论如何都无法享受到同样的日光的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.52,0:21:20.75,main,Wis,0,0,0,,但这又有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.37,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我们就像这样慢慢的，小心翼翼的就行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:30.31,main,Wis,0,0,0,,我们有同伴，有可以共度良宵的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:37.22,main,Wis,0,0,0,,现在这样与你同行的日子，我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:40.73,main,Wis,0,0,0,,谢谢你，Marbas
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:48.66,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,我也是，谢谢你找到我，Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:50.47,main,Naberius,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.47,0:21:52.74,main,Diana,0,0,0,,到出发的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.79,0:21:54.80,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,Wisteria
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.32,0:22:00.50,main,Wis,0,0,0,,今晚月色真美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:03.00,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,啊，今晚月色真美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.42,0:22:05.18,main,Marbas,0,0,0,,风也温柔
